TabLIST - Limit the maximum number of tabs and block unwanted websites.

An extension designed to help you improve your productivity and concentration while you work and study. By limiting the number of open tabs and blocking unwanted websites, TabLIST helps you stay focused on your tasks and make the most of your time.

A simple, intuitive, user-friendly, secure, and safe interface that anyone can use with ease.
